{"tid":464748,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【原來係你】《賭神3》演菲律賓賭神 胡慧沖被劇組暗譏「冇人識」","createTime":"2017-11-10T23:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T00:08:51.000Z","uid":32938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9239ae79cc0a57ca0ca06f516f6825e6cb741a9a","tid":464748,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171017/large/1508245285_fe64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171017%2Flarge%2F1508245285_fe64.jpg&h=525b91bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171017/large/1508245291_ae63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171017%2Flarge%2F1508245291_ae63.jpg&h=2c1306c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡慧沖Roger喺做旅遊達人之前，原來做過幕後，又拍過電影，而佢嘅處女作就係陳嘉上執導嘅《飛虎》。正所謂一不離二，之後Roger拍過唔少作品，佢話：「拍完呢套之後，有朋友介紹我去拍陳果嗰套《香港製造》，之後又再拍《賭神3之少年賭神》，最後一套係《非常警察》。」<br />\n<br />\n不過佢就話其實當年拍戲都有唔開心嘅回憶，佢話當年拍《賭神3之少年賭神》演菲律賓賭神時：「可能我始終唔係電影出身，有時去到片場，明星坐埋一堆，我一個人又唔知點樣，好記得有一次，嗰陣拍《少年賭神》，我已經自己帶咗支水，但係都會飲晒，所以咪自己走去斟水，點知個阿姐話唔怪之得冇得咁快，連你都走嚟斟！」<br />\n<br />\n嗰一刻Roger即刻不是味兒，仲話感覺勁hurt：「事後我喺個露台諗我究竟係乜嘢？係個乞衣？話晒我喺亞視都係做高級編審，點解我要做啲咁嘅嘢，最後我安慰自己話始終唔係藝人，又唔係一個拍電影嘅人才，做娛樂圈要有好多關係，玩就OK，拍完都冇乜心機，拍完玩過咪算！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然keep住阿Q精神，不過Roger話可能自己啲戲實在太屎，之後已經冇人搵拍戲：「人生做過就算，不在其位，不謀其政，你問我會唔會返轉頭，我諗唔會喇，我個樣可以好兇狠，但係講嘢太斯文，又唔打得又唔惡得，費事令人覺得失望。當然如果將來有啲角色唔係做壞人，可能係做慈父又或者弱智嗰啲，都可以玩吓。」"},{"pid":"4cae43b46b2d3143c1e02873dbaa31f5e4129840","tid":464748,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b3eb11f7f00667c4f643d8fecb883b7187b66e","tid":464748,"uid":49004,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:26:37.000Z","msg":"我留番雙手揸波好過"},{"pid":"cc230e068a7bca48a2368aedb3b143bd7a0b329a","tid":464748,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06874a5f225a851d3678e65c42820b0c3718bda0","tid":464748,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:54:48.000Z","msg":"真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd59fef5705d4253c773ca3275f5e40a41699adc","tid":464748,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T23:57:05.000Z","msg":"竟然係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf740b2ba75cbaf6c31fddaaf9f3457e3708035","tid":464748,"uid":19322,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:06:48.000Z","msg":"我三條K都費事去丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27154a5f211c613f6ad6eca00ee39e0f6992d630","tid":464748,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我留番雙手揸波好過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}